1089_134691_000006_000000 --Whose feet are as the feet of harts and underneath the everlasting arms.
1089_134691_000007_000000 The pride of that dim image brought back to his mind the dignity of the office he had refused.
1089_134691_000007_000001 All through his boyhood he had mused upon that which he had so often thought to be his destiny and when the moment had come for him to obey the call he had turned aside, obeying a wayward instinct.
