3005_163389_000011_000001 I could a stayed if I wanted to, but I didn't want to.
3005_163389_000012_000000 I went to the circus and loafed around the back side till the watchman went by, and then dived in under the tent.
3005_163389_000012_000002 You can't be too careful.
3005_163389_000013_000000 It was a real bully circus.
3005_163389_000014_000001 And so one after the other they all skipped off into the ring, and made the sweetest bow I ever see, and then scampered out, and everybody clapped their hands and went just about wild.
3005_163389_000015_000000 Well, all through the circus they done the most astonishing things; and all the time that clown carried on so it most killed the people.
3005_163389_000015_000008 It warn't funny to me, though; I was all of a tremble to see his danger. But pretty soon he struggled up astraddle and grabbed the bridle, a reeling this way and that; and the next minute he sprung up and dropped the bridle and stood! and the horse a going like a house afire too.
3005_163389_000015_000010 He shed them so thick they kind of clogged up the air, and altogether he shed seventeen suits.
3005_163389_000015_000011 And, then, there he was, slim and handsome, and dressed the gaudiest and prettiest you ever saw, and he lit into that horse with his whip and made him fairly hum  and finally skipped off, and made his bow and danced off to the dressing room, and everybody just a howling with pleasure and astonishment.
3005_163389_000016_000001 Why, it was one of his own men!
3005_163389_000016_000002 He had got up that joke all out of his own head, and never let on to nobody.
3005_163389_000016_000004 I don't know; there may be bullier circuses than what that one was, but I never struck them yet.
3005_163389_000017_000001 And they laughed all the time, and that made the duke mad; and everybody left, anyway, before the show was over, but one boy which was asleep.
3005_163389_000017_000002 So the duke said these Arkansaw lunkheads couldn't come up to Shakespeare; what they wanted was low comedy  and maybe something ruther worse than low comedy, he reckoned.
3005_163389_000017_000003 He said he could size their style.
