3005_163390_000001_000000 CHAPTER twenty three.
3005_163390_000002_000000 WELL, all day him and the king was hard at it, rigging up a stage and a curtain and a row of candles for footlights; and that night the house was jam full of men in no time.
3005_163390_000002_000002 And  but never mind the rest of his outfit; it was just wild, but it was awful funny.
