3528_168656_000003_000000 In the Little Convent there was a centenarian who came from the Abbey of Fontevrault.
3528_168656_000003_000001 She had even been in society before the Revolution.
3528_168656_000003_000003 She told wonders of the Abbey of Fontevrault,--that it was like a city, and that there were streets in the monastery.
3528_168656_000004_000000 She talked with a Picard accent which amused the pupils.
3528_168656_000005_000000 On another occasion, the centenarian was telling stories.
3528_168656_000005_000001 She said that in her youth the Bernardine monks were every whit as good as the mousquetaires.
3528_168656_000005_000002 It was a century which spoke through her, but it was the eighteenth century.
3528_168656_000005_000003 She told about the custom of the four wines, which existed before the Revolution in Champagne and Bourgogne.
3528_168656_000005_000004 When a great personage, a marshal of France, a prince, a duke, and a peer, traversed a town in Burgundy or Champagne, the city fathers came out to harangue him and presented him with four silver gondolas into which they had poured four different sorts of wine.
3528_168656_000005_000005 On the first goblet this inscription could be read, monkey wine; on the second, lion wine; on the third, sheep wine; on the fourth, hog wine.
3528_168656_000006_000000 In a cupboard, under lock and key, she kept a mysterious object of which she thought a great deal.
3528_168656_000006_000001 The rule of Fontevrault did not forbid this. She would not show this object to anyone.
3528_168656_000006_000002 She shut herself up, which her rule allowed her to do, and hid herself, every time that she desired to contemplate it.
3528_168656_000006_000003 If she heard a footstep in the corridor, she closed the cupboard again as hastily as it was possible with her aged hands.
3528_168656_000006_000005 The most curious were baffled by her silence and the most tenacious by her obstinacy.
3528_168656_000006_000006 Thus it furnished a subject of comment for all those who were unoccupied or bored in the convent.
3528_168656_000006_000008 Some unique chaplet?
3528_168656_000006_000009 Some authentic relic? They lost themselves in conjectures.
3528_168656_000006_000011 They found the object beneath a triple linen cloth, like some consecrated paten.
