6938_70848_000105_000002 If we are broken, then it will be in defending our flag...."
6938_70848_000109_000001 "I greet you with the christening of a new Russian life and freedom!"
7018_75789_000000_000000 When it was the Five Hundred and Sixty first Night,
7018_75789_000001_000003 Then I loaded it with the goods, precious ores and jewels: and the union pearls which were like gravel and the best of the ambergris crude and pure, together with what I had collected on the island and what was left me of victual and wild herbs.
7018_75789_000001_000004 Lastly I lashed a piece of wood on either side, to serve me as oars; and launched it, and embarking, did according to the saying of the poet,
7018_75789_000003_000000 My boat raft drifted with the stream, I pondering the issue of my affair; and the drifting ceased not till I came to the place where it disappeared beneath the mountain.
7018_75789_000003_000005 But I was delighted at my escape from the river.
