7018_75789_000004_000000 When it was the Five Hundred and Sixty second Night,
7018_75789_000005_000002 So I consorted with the chief of the islanders, and they paid me the utmost respect.
7018_75789_000005_000006 One day, the King himself asked me of the fashions and form of government of my country, and I acquainted him with the circumstance of the Caliph's sway in the city of Baghdad and the justice of his rule.
7018_75789_000005_000009 Then he bestowed on me great riches from his treasuries and charged me with a magnificent present for the Caliph Harun al Rashid.
7018_75789_000005_000010 Moreover he gave me a sealed letter, saying, "Carry this with thine own hand to the Commander of the Faithful and give him many salutations from us!" "Hearing and obedience," I replied.
