8131_117029_000017_000001 It was almost good to get out into the filth of the slums, and be heading back to the still standing monument of the old Chicken Coop.
8131_117029_000017_000002 He headed for the private entrance out of habit, and then shrugged as he realized it was a needless precaution now.
8131_117029_000017_000003 He moved up the front steps and through the battered seal.
