8455_210777_000023_000001 A presentiment indeed!
8455_210777_000023_000002 How much of evil,--of real accomplished evil,--had there not occurred to me during the last few days!
8455_210777_000023_000003 Every hope for which I had lived, as I then told myself, had been brought to sudden extinction by the coming of these men to whom I had been so pleasant, and who, in their turn, had been so pleasant to me!
8455_210777_000023_000009 When this captain should have taken himself and his vessel back to England, I would retire to a small farm which I possessed at the farthest side of the island, and there in seclusion would I end my days.
8455_210777_000023_000010 Mrs Neverbend should come with me, or stay, if it so pleased her, in Gladstonopolis.
