8555_284449_000058_000000 Then the Room of the Great Knife was cleared of its awful furniture.
8555_284449_000058_000002 All the rubbish was piled in the square before the palace and a bonfire made of it, while the Blue people clustered around and danced and sang with joy as the blue flames devoured the dreadful instrument that had once caused them so much unhappiness.
8555_284449_000059_000001 The combined bands of both the countries played the music and a fine supper was served.
